{"tid":1686654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望聽日大家抱住呢個心態出嚟活動","createTime":"2019-11-01T09:38:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T11:53:05.000Z","uid":77393,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"457b34952380c8be8bac88c3dbeb4a58bb3c9576","tid":1686654,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:38:34.000Z","msg":"雖然有多個集會不反對通知書<br />\n但班popo濫權濫捕已經唔係新鮮事<br />\n如果大家身邊冇足夠人數支持 保持低調 唔希望再有手足送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇錯 我哋係行使緊香港市民應有嘅基本權利  再加幾張不反對通知 實際上係popo冇理由搞我哋<br />\n<br />\n但而家嘅香港已經冇法治可言 如果大家仍然抱住自己係合情合法所以冇任何風險<br />\n咁其實係反映你對林奠正苦同警隊相當信任 同我哋爭取革命背後其實好矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以 大家每個行動都要諗清楚自己同身邊嘅人承唔承受到風險後果 再決定自己嘅抗爭模式<br />\n<br />\n無論大家選擇邊個角色 你都絕對係其中一分子 絕對係對革命有幫助 最重要係留得青山在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁多位手足 聽日 11.2 3pm 維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"0e60568af004cc3e4b9dbd37658a981500cb2541","tid":1686654,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:38:55.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"fbe21fb52d5c64307effe30096528f49ca4f55f8","tid":1686654,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:41:38.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"335c81e0965055bb1f95870cb02910eef9f958fa","tid":1686654,"uid":60408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:42:53.000Z","msg":"要保持警覺，多留意有無警車係附近<br />\n明明合法但都要小心呀大家"},{"pid":"fc946b0a701b06040e8bed950df71a671ebf259a","tid":1686654,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:45:04.000Z","msg":"112維園見<br />\n【突發】11月2活動需要大量文宣，你我都做到<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/erxDBS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/erxDBS</a>"},{"pid":"e516fe35f29945f197f84b1be0fbe6d86c4b7bf9","tid":1686654,"uid":196678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:00:42.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"3d5cdfd4b8442d04f482665e536b0d3cd660e6dc","tid":1686654,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:04:54.000Z","msg":"甴近平3/10"},{"pid":"fc0d6d7e64442c43bc1e138528fa9072bbb3b8df","tid":1686654,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:09:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b59a625f4e3e397ed00954a3b41cb34937d3aea6","tid":1686654,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:10:35.000Z","msg":"正經post 無人推<br />\n返工能唔係吹風我真係唔能信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf54a8126be40826d9a68daca54e0811ca871f0","tid":1686654,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:12:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zk7OKku.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzk7OKku.png&h=809cfe9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b90afd1e6bdd835833f6b8694811d49d3eef087","tid":1686654,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T11:52:21.000Z","msg":"甴近平4/10"},{"pid":"aaa80e14a6eecdcacab80b10d4a68ed6d6e4a2e9","tid":1686654,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b59a625f4e3e397ed00954a3b41cb34937d3aea6","tid":1686654,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:10:35.000Z","msg":"正經post 無人推<br />\n返工能唔係吹風我真係唔能信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T11:53:05.000Z","msg":"連登仔只係鍾意政治抽水 互屌 希望發放多啲正能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}